nodes.text: This trader was a female Hig, a slender blue-skinned species. She owned an automated ore hauler which, in 24 ABY, she donated to the Diversity Alliance, a pro-alien, anti-Human organization. While she occasionally piloted the ship herself, she preferred to let the autopilot control most cargo runs, instead spending her time relaxing in a cantina on a backwater planet.
Her ore hauler was used by four members of the Jedi Praxeum on Yavin 4 to infiltrate the Diversity Alliance operations on the planet Ryloth.
